{"tid":415840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國樂器選擇一問","createTime":"2017-09-27T10:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T14:40:41.000Z","uid":84524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5733b45fba1f219dc56ae7f8adeed04937693b6d","tid":415840,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:03:41.000Z","msg":"話說小弟我以前俾老母逼學長笛學到厭，辛辛苦苦咁考到8級之後就冇再拎起之笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，而我阿媽就日日都煩住叫我用8級長笛去教人順便賺吓錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ( 我自己連長笛都唔鍾意仲點會有心機教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n而最近我喺 YouTube 咁啱睇到一個 channel 係笛子&amp; 蕭嘅演奏，嗰種中國風嘅味道真係好正，所以想用自己賺嘅錢學吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問吓有冇手足對呢兩種樂器係有啲認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想聽吓你地嘅意見同埋對嗰種樂器嘅評語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37f99b32e8d0ac340fb991e9c8e340e6f523348","tid":415840,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:16:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">支</span>笛， sorry 自膠"},{"pid":"34a0af3ef8a711f9d47c9111be4e5db8f9064258","tid":415840,"uid":71594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"留tg畀我 我教笛子"},{"pid":"3636af82c82fc55c20bd456ba3e3de9ea56ea23e","tid":415840,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留tg畀我 我教笛子</blockquote><br />\n巴打有心，不過我仲猶疑緊學邊個好，想集合吓其他意見再決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過之前都搵過吓資料，笛子有唔同種類 (曲笛，梆笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)仲有唔同調，咁玩起嚟係咪要好多支笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659e7540c13d43eab74d1314f80aabdad5b00e3e","tid":415840,"uid":126540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留tg畀我 我教笛子</blockquote><br />\n巴打有心，不過我仲猶疑緊學邊個好，想集合吓其他意見再決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過之前都搵過吓資料，笛子有唔同種類 (曲笛，梆笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)仲有唔同調，咁玩起嚟係咪要好多支笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 有時要換"},{"pid":"9222d557eaf5afb7e9f404adfb072fc10353f52b","tid":415840,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T12:04:11.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，亦都歡迎有玩笛/蕭 以外中樂嘅巴絲入黎分享吓心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0104c88dba6cb04a7f3d8828f7f7e46855c9831","tid":415840,"uid":71594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:46:59.000Z","msg":"咁我喺到講 <br />\n我覺得你可以自己平平地買支G調試下<br />\n有長笛底好易上手"},{"pid":"7d8ad5bcba50a60cfa658f2398cc7a2741fc8a46","tid":415840,"uid":125163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:52:13.000Z","msg":"巴打其實可以諗下玩樂團，入面乜樂器都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d3f6975c2d65a5b6a32704b61c663e4c62bf8d","tid":415840,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:39:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打其實可以諗下玩樂團，入面乜樂器都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係咩都唔識都入到去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9669cfd8826759702f0017d60d8d05b8110a7289","tid":415840,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁我喺到講 <br />\n我覺得你可以自己平平地買支G調試下<br />\n有長笛底好易上手</blockquote><br />\n多謝提議，得閒買支撚吓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac